Synopses :

* A bureaucrat in a retro-future world tries to correct an administrative error
and himself becomes an enemy of the state. 

*  Sam Lowry is a harried technocrat in a futuristic society that is needlessly
convoluted and inefficient. He dreams of a life where he can fly away from
technology and overpowering bureaucracy, and spend eternity with the woman
of his dreams.

* The film centres on a man trying to find a woman who appears in his dreams
while he is working in a mind-numbing job and living a life in a small
apartment, set in a dystopian world in which there is an over-reliance on
poorly maintained (and rather whimsical) machines.


Crew :
Director - Terry Gilliam
Writers - Terry Gilliam, Tom Stoppard &amp; Charles McKeown + one
Original Music - Michael Kamen
Cinematography - Roger Pratt

